1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on training ResNet-50 on ImageNet, which is a popular dataset in computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses several techniques used to maintain accuracy with a large minibatch size, which is a common problem in machine learning. 
3. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper describes the hardware and software system used to achieve the performance, which involves a large number of GPUs. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the use of RMSprop and batch normalization, which are commonly used in neural network training. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses techniques used to improve the efficiency of training ResNet-50, which is a popular deep learning architecture used in various AI applications.
